data.description: Come see this perfect family home in the quiet subdivision of Glen Meadow.  This home has a large living area to entertain.  The kitchen is very light and bright with granite countertops, white subway backsplash and a gas stove.  There is dark laminate flooring throughout the main living area, recently replaced fixtures and ceiling fans.  Huge fenced back yard with a nice tree line behind the back fence as well.  Seller will allow concessions for roof repairs.  This is a must-see, perfect for all families.  Contact your favorite agent today to schedule your appointment.
